title: GameStop Bails on Crypto Gaming, Killing NFT Marketplace
description: The news comes four months after the storied video game retailer axed its NFT wallet, with GameStop set to exit the space entirely.

title: Senator Elizabeth Warren Says SEC Is Wrong for Approving Spot Bitcoin ETFs
description: U.S. Senator Elizabeth Warren has slammed the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) for approving spot bitcoin exchange-traded funds (ETFs).
